name: My Own World
content: I got my own world on my hands
我手里握着我的小世界
I put my DJ on the house
I got my own world on my hands
我手里握着我的小世界
I put my DJ on the house
Just hold me in your arms
And when your dream will be over
Drop everything and let me in
放弃一切 让我进来
And let me do my shops
Stay close to me and people dream
